PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1990-6/799 that will increase the maximum amount payable under the terms of a contract awarded to DUPONT DESMEULES/SANDWELL in 1990 for the provision of project management services and construction supervision in connection with ALOUETTE PROJECT at the Port of Sept-Îles, Quebec, and will change the name of the contractor to Dupont Desmeules et Associés Inc.
